                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <desc type="ProtectivePrayer">
                      <locus target="#11r #50r" facs="013 052">Fols. 11r, 50r</locus> Prayer to protect a woman from a lover.
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">
                        ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ማዕሠረ፡ ፍቅ፡ ረፊቀ፡ ተሐቂቅ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>[በ]ዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ፡ እስር፡ ወከንትር፡ ከናፍረ፡ ሕልጻ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                      </foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                      <locus target="#ir(ecto)" facs="001">Fol. ir(ecto)</locus>, Note of ownership, name insufficiently legible
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <desc>
                      Blank: <locus target="#iv(erso) #iir(ecto)" facs="002">fols. iv(erso), iir(ecto)</locus>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a3">
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                      <locus target="#1r" facs="003"> f. 1r, (upper margin)</locus> Note of ownership: “This book belongs to Gäbäyähu.” <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገበየሁ፡</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a4">
                    <desc type="RecordReconciliation">
                      <locus target="#79v" facs="082">Fol. 79v</locus>: Decision of Reconciliation for a Dispute, including  witnesses
                      <foreign xml:lang="am">
                        ጥጥብል፡ በተጣሉበት፡ በአቶ፡ አበበ፡ እርሻ፡ ገቢያውና፡ ካሳው፡<lb/>
                        ሲታረቁ፡ የዘመድ፡ ዳኛው፡ ይቤ፡ ሰሎሞን፡ የዘመዱ፡ እማኞች፡<lb/>
                        አዱኛ፡ ገብሬ፡ አቶ፡ ጌታሁን፡ ፈረደ፡ ገበዘ፡ ቄስ፡ ይባርክ፡ የዘንድሮን፡<lb/>
                        አለባ፡ ካሳው፡ በልቶ፡ ሊለቅ፡ በዚህ፡ ታርቀዋል። ፲፱፴፪፡ አመተ፡<lb/>
                        ምሕረት፡ ማዝያ፡ በዘመነ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ፭፡ ቀን፡ ተጻፈ። ። ። ባላንጋራው፡<lb/>
                        ካሳው፡ እንዳለው፡ ወዶ፡ መዝገቡን፡ ከገብያው፡ ይቀመጥ፡ ብለዋል፡<lb/>
                        ይህን፡ እማኞች፡ ሰምተዋል፡ ጸሐፊሁ፡ መኳንንት፡ ወንድም፡ አገኘሁ፡<lb/>
                        ሽመላ፡ ማርያም፡
                      </foreign>
                      When Gäbiyaw and Kasaw disputed about the farm of Ato Abäbä,
                      the family judge was Yǝbe Solomon. The witnesses were Aduñña
                      Gäbǝre and Ato Getahun Färädä. May the priest bless this decision
                      [?]. They agreed for Kassaw to take this year’s harvest and leave the
                      land. It is written in 1932, year of mercy, Miyazya, in the year of
                      John, [the Evangelist]. The disputant, Kassaw, agreed that the
                      document will stay in the hand of Gäbiyaw. And the witnesses were
                      present. The scribe is Mäkwanǝnt Wändǝm Agäñähu of Šǝmäla
                      Maryam
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a5">
                    <desc type="Genealogy">
                      <locus target="#80r #80v" facs="082 083">Fols. 80r, 80v</locus>, Genealogical List (described in the plates catalog)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                      <desc>
                        Scribal intervention:
                        words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#7r #25v #37v #52r #55r" facs="009 028 040 054 057">folss. 7r, 25v, 37v, 52r, 55r, </locus>, etc.);
                        erasure markings are visible (<locus target="#49v" facs="052">49v</locus>)
                      </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
                  </additions>
